{"tid":854893,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信保護戴伟浚国籍及正名 [更新版]","createTime":"2018-10-09T16:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T00:06:40.000Z","uid":27939,"like":69,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e85c2dca87a284d6eef8b5c57b3888e31d125897","tid":854893,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:27:40.000Z","msg":"Dear Sir/Madam,<br />\n<br />\nI, as a Hong-Konger, completely sorry to write this letter to tell, your player &ldquo;Dai&rdquo; should not be listed as a Hong Kong player.<br />\n<br />\nDue to the recent international duty call, &ldquo;Dai&rdquo; had chosen to play for Chinese U21, instead of Hong Kong senior team, which are completely two different nationalities. I am deeply disappointed to tell you that please do not list Mr. Dai as a Hong-Konger. For the moment he chose to play for Chinese team, he shall lose his right to own the British Citizen as well. And you may need to rearrange the working permission from the Government. <br />\n<br />\nPersonally would suggest that you shall correct the spelling for &ldquo;Mr. Dai&rdquo; from the original Hong Kong style to the following Mandarin style, &ldquo;D&agrave;i Wěi J&ugrave;n&rdquo;. As Chinese people are quite sensitive on nationality, if you keep making mistake on Mr. D&agrave;i Wěi J&ugrave;n nationality and name, that would be a huge political disaster.<br />\n<br />\nMoreover, after correcting the spelling and nationality, you shall also consider the professionalism of Mr. D&agrave;i Wěi J&ugrave;n. Rejecting a senior national team call and chose to TRAIN with a youth team, in my unprofessional opinion, the club is the one who pay for the player, not the youth team. Team always comes in front of players, how could Mr. D&agrave;i Wěi J&ugrave;n put a youth team training call come higher than the team, plus he is not doing really well in your team. This is a disgrace and disrespectful behaviour as a professional football player. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKing Regards,<br />\nFellaini the Tree"},{"pid":"c019c6830fde6ddf1e0dcbb9e7ea14f480a76eb1","tid":854893,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091af70964cd64c44640c9eb656e3d8dd6e5a56b","tid":854893,"uid":38189,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:32:25.000Z","msg":"Fellaini the Tree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b48a22733646c6bf1062dd00684640c185c2ba4","tid":854893,"uid":8968,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGoodest English"},{"pid":"3937cd913c15376e2addda940c966375bdbebddc","tid":854893,"uid":27939,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:34:12.000Z","msg":"可以send去<br />\n牛津聯既Communication Manager  <br />\nChris Williams<br />\ncwilliams@oufc.co.uk<br />\n<br />\n或<br />\n<br />\n大粒d既Managing Director <br />\nNiall Williams <br />\nnmcwilliams@oufc.co.uk<br />\n<br />\nCopy and paste 個內容改返個名就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7d42d87c1d6d4558901541dd5c289c7317311c","tid":854893,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:34:22.000Z","msg":"好難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42da3c52ea7f8f105166896704a99088d1d1fa26","tid":854893,"uid":27866,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:36:04.000Z","msg":"proofread 下先啦"},{"pid":"3c680ffb0477ff805dc430467f81e4463f607362","tid":854893,"uid":4260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:38:43.000Z","msg":"King Regards,<br />\nFellaini the Tree<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9b39c4398a779011a251669c8bf1c1a5fd